				<div class="header">What is WarnerMedia Alerts?</div>
					<div class="sub-header">WarnerMedia Alerts is an emergency notification system available to all staff and most non-staff. WarnerMedia may issue emergency notifications, public safety alerts and other important messages relevant to work at HBO and the HBO workplace.<br/> <br/>If you work in a facility or building maintained by another business unit, such as Warner Bros., your information may be shared — and you may also receive pertinent workplace-related notifications from — one of the other units.          </div>
			</td>
	   </tr>
	   <tr>
			<td>
				<div class="header">How does it work?</div>
					<div class="sub-header">In the event of an emergency or safety threat, HBO will send you important safety updates via phone, text, email or desktop alert. <i>Please note: Message and data rates may apply.</i>	   </div>
			</td>
	   </tr>
	   <tr>
			<td>
				<div class="header">From what phone number will I receive calls?</div>
